    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have got to see this beauty\u2014it\u2019s honestly in such incredible shape, you\u2019d think it just rolled off the showroom floor today! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it runs like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s practically perfect and ready for its next adventure, this is definitely the one for you. It's been my pride and joy, but it's time for someone else to enjoy it. Feel free to reach out if you want to take a look!",
      "price": 46500.0,
