    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, collector-grade vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. This car has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage and has never seen a day of inclement weather. The exterior paint retains its deep, glass-like luster thanks to a professional-grade ceramic coating, and the body is entirely free of stone chips, door dings, or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin is absolutely pristine; the premium leather upholstery remains firm and supple with zero wear on the bolsters, and the original floor mats are spotless. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the climate control, functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, the vehicle is beyond reproach, featuring a comprehensive service history performed exclusively by master technicians using OEM parts. With low mileage and a flawless undercarriage, this is a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle in impeccable condition that will satisfy even the most fastidious buyer.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are proud to present this exemplary motorcar, maintained to the most exacting standards of automotive excellence. This vehicle represents a rare acquisition opportunity, remaining in absolute showroom condition with no discernible wear. From the flawless paint depth to the factory-fresh interior appointments, every detail confirms its status as a premier specimen. Mechanically beyond reproach and aesthetically perfect, this vehicle is offered for the discerning driver who demands nothing less than the pinnacle of its class.",
      "price": 48950.0,
