    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you\u2014she\u2019s a total dream! This car has been pampered since day one and honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. No scratches, no spills, just pure perfection. It drives like a cloud and has been kept in a climate-controlled garage. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the dealership headache, you\u2019ve found it! Come take a look, you won\u2019t be disappointed!",
      "price": 44900.0,
