    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 1997 Carrera represents the pinnacle of air-cooled engineering. Powered by the 3.6L flat-six featuring the Varioram induction system for optimized mid-range torque, it is paired with a crisp Getrag G50 6-speed manual transaxle. The mechanical integrity is superlative, featuring a dry crankcase, original factory-spec multi-link rear geometry, and four-piston Monobloc calipers providing phenomenal bite. This is a collector-grade example with zero oxidative wear on the undercarriage, pristine synchros, and all original VIN-matching body panels. A mechanically flawless survivor for the serious petrolhead.",
